rComments: By far the best Professor I have had in 6 years of undergrad. She goes above and beyond to help her students both in lecture and during office hours. She has such a great passion for her field, and the personal anecdotes that she uses helps to immerse the class further. Just lovely overall and I would highly encourage anyone to take her courses.

She is pretty good and knows her stuff. Really friendly and helpful. Sometimes she kind of gets excited and has a cute nervousness while speaking (I assume because her native tongue is not English). But she is really great and you won't regret taking her courses.
Milena is a very good professor. She is very knowledgeable on the field of late Ottoman Empire and modern Balkan history. You won't regret taking her courses :)
Great prof. Really nice and helpful. Topic itself is pretty niche and dull (the history part) but she makes it interesting.
